<span id="freeTextContainer17085580458087014099"><b>Not gonna lie, I had to push myself to get through this.</b><br/><br/>I just didn’t find it enjoyable in the slightest, which makes me feel like a loser since it’s such a beloved children’s classic.<br/><br/>But at least I’m an honest loser?<br/><br/>I didn’t really like Peter.<br/>Wendy annoyed me.<br/>And the humor and tone just fell flat for me.<br/><br/>But, on the plus side, at least I can count this as my first completed classic for the year. This was supposed to be my January read and it’s now February...but who’s counting.<br/><br/>Me, that’s who. On</span>
