  <span id="freeText6701283933940776280" style="display:none">Reread #2<br />This is still my favorite book. It's whimsical, beautiful, heart-warming, heart-wrenching, dark... it's wonderful. I love it so much.<br />---------------------------------------<br /><br />Upon Reread:<br />It's even better the second time. I will never stop rereading this book. It's so important to me and I don't even know why. Walt Disney, I've always loved you, but I'm never touching merch that reflects your version of this story. Nothing can compare.<br /><br />----------------------------------------<br /><br />This is one of my new favorite books. it's hillarious, it's heart tugging, it's one that I'll go back to many many times. I'm so happy I read the original story.</span>
